item.title: Initial Commit
item.author: jd.hernandez@gmail.com (Jorge Hernandez)
item.description: Initial commit. Barebones, no code other than those from the frameworks used. A slate, not clean, but prepared, upon which to build. That’s what that commit message has always meant for me. So it is with this blog.
